  <brief_title>Effect of Mitomycin C on Urethral Stricture Recurrence After Internal Urethrotomy</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Hillel Yaffe Medical Center</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Hillel Yaffe Medical Center</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of local injected mitomycin C at the time
      of internal urethrotomy in order to prevent the recurrence of urethral strictures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
